g `v0.2.0` (no tag conflict)\n\n## ⚠️ Not done automatically (needs approval)\n- **Push commit + tag to remote** and **publish the GitHub release** — outward-facing, flagged for review below.\n- ⚠️ Open security findings against this tree are **not** resolved by this release: no-auth dev-tenant seam (`src/lib/tenant.ts`), full-document CourtListener egress (`src/lib/citations/verify.ts:142`), and transitive `postcss <8.5.10` XSS. These were noted in the CHANGELOG and remain tracked separately — **review before deploying this tag.**", "content_type": "success", "priority": "normal"}}

